article_title: Humana fined after KY Department of Insurance investigation
article_text: A film about an FBI agent who pleaded guilty in Kentucky to strangling an informant in 1989 is scheduled to begin shooting this week in Lexington.

article_metadata.Description: The Kentucky Department of Insurance fined the Louisville based company over $65,000 for the incident.
